column5:
As some of you may remember, we brought some tadpoles home from a local conservation area to try and raise to frogs. My little one wants to take them back to the pond we got them from once they are big enough. Here's some new pics...


Here's a short hilarious movie...just listen to what my little has to say...haha. They are eating on an algae wafer...their choice of food in our place.
Daplumma uses a rod and reel to catch those things with!!!  ... what did y'all use?
HAHAHAHAHAHA   Good job, guys! I hate when I see those critters leaving the French restaurants by the back door in wheelchairs though.
